title EXACT 2026 Pipeline

direction right

User Input [icon: file-text, color: blue] {
  Single Input [label: "Single input\n--input JSON or raw question"]
  Batch Input [label: "Batch input\n--input_file JSONL"]
}

CLI [icon: terminal, label: "run.py\nCLI entrypoint"]

Router [icon: split, color: purple] {
  Route [label: "router.py\nroute_and_run()"]
  Subtask Classifier [label: "domain_classifier.py\nclassify_subtask()"]
}

Physics Pipeline [icon: atom, color: green] {
  Physics Orchestrator [label: "pipeline_physics.py\nrun_physics()"]
  Domain Classifier [label: "classify_domain()\ncircuit / electrostatics / energy / general"]
  Direct Solver [label: "direct_solver.py\ntry_direct_solve()"]
  Formula Retrieval [label: "formula_db.py\nretrieve_formulas()"]
  Physics Prompt [label: "prompts.py\nbuild_physics_prompt()"]
  Numeric Parser [label: "answer_parser.py\nparse_answer()"]
  Unit Normalizer [label: "unit_normalizer.py\nnormalize_unit()\nexpand_prefix()"]
  Numeric Vote [label: "voting.py\nrelative-tolerance clustering\nmedian winner"]
  Physics Output [label: "Physics result\nanswer, unit, explanation,\ncot, confidence, debug"]
}

Education Pipeline [icon: book-open, color: orange] {
  Edu Orchestrator [label: "pipeline_edu.py\nrun_edu()"]
  Edu Prompt [label: "prompts.py\nbuild_edu_prompt()"]
  Logic Answer Parser [label: "ANSWER line parser\nYes / No / True / False / A-D"]
  Majority Vote [label: "Exact-string majority vote"]
  Edu Output [label: "Edu result\nanswer, explanation,\ncot, premises, confidence,\nfol placeholder"]
}

LLM Layer [icon: cpu, color: gray] {
  VLLM Client [label: "inference.py\nVLLMClient"]
  Generate One [label: "generate_one()\nOpenAI chat completion"]
  Generate K [label: "generate_k()\nparallel self-consistency"]
  VLLM Server [icon: server, label: "vLLM server\nOpenAI-compatible /v1"]
  Inference Model [icon: brain, label: "deepseek-ai/DeepSeek-R1-0528-Qwen3-8B"]
}

Training Pipeline [icon: database, color: yellow] {
  Local Dataset [label: "dataset/\nBTC physics + BTC logic"]
  Data Config [label: "train/data_config.py\nsource configs"]
  Prepare Data [label: "train/prepare_data.py\nfilter, normalize, ChatML export"]
  SFT JSONL [label: "output/data/*.jsonl\ntrain/dev/test"]
  LoRA Train [label: "train/train_lora.py\nTRL SFTTrainer + PEFT LoRA"]
  Adapter [label: "output/lora\nLoRA adapter"]
  Merge LoRA [label: "train/merge_lora.py\nmerge adapter into base"]
  Merged Model [label: "output/merged\nserve with vLLM"]
}

Contest Output [icon: check-circle, color: blue, label: "Contest JSON\nanswer, explanation, cot,\nfol, premises, confidence"]

Single Input > CLI
Batch Input > CLI
CLI > Route
Route > Subtask Classifier

Subtask Classifier > Physics Orchestrator: "question only -> Subtask 2"
Subtask Classifier > Edu Orchestrator: "premises-NL / premises_nl -> Subtask 1"

Physics Orchestrator > Domain Classifier
Physics Orchestrator > Direct Solver: "optional direct_first"
Physics Orchestrator > Formula Retrieval
Formula Retrieval > Physics Prompt
Physics Prompt > Generate K

Edu Orchestrator > Edu Prompt
Edu Prompt > Generate K

Generate K > Generate One
Generate One > VLLM Client
VLLM Client > VLLM Server
VLLM Server > Inference Model
Inference Model > VLLM Server
VLLM Server > VLLM Client
VLLM Client > Generate One
Generate One > Generate K

Generate K > Numeric Parser: "physics generations"
Numeric Parser > Unit Normalizer
Unit Normalizer > Numeric Vote
Direct Solver > Physics Output: "fast direct result or refinement"
Numeric Vote > Physics Output

Generate K > Logic Answer Parser: "edu generations"
Logic Answer Parser > Majority Vote
Majority Vote > Edu Output

Physics Output > Contest Output
Edu Output > Contest Output

Local Dataset > Data Config
Data Config > Prepare Data
Prepare Data > SFT JSONL
SFT JSONL > LoRA Train
LoRA Train > Adapter
Adapter > Merge LoRA
Merge LoRA > Merged Model
Merged Model > VLLM Server: "replace model path when serving"
